data.description: WELCOME HOME! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2 bath RANCH has charming curb appeal & has already undergone extensive EXTERIOR renovations; (over $80k!) replacing all the big ticket items! The interior still awaits your personal touch & creative vision (needs flooring, paint, cabinets etc). The extensive list of NEW items in 2014 include: NEW ROOF, SIDING, GUTTERS, FASCIA, VINYL CLAD WINDOWS, AND $23k worth of concrete work; (new driveway & garage floor). Water heater (2022), leaf filters (2021), HVAC (approx. 2003/2004). Outside, the private backyard oasis is FENCED IN, & boasts a 2 car garage AND storage shed, even a sidewalk to the front AND back doors. With a blank canvas that still needs work on the inside, this home presents a unique opportunity to update the interior to suit your personal style. Featuring 3 ample sized bedrooms including a primary suite with a full second bathroom, the open concept living/dining room features a wall of windows & natural light; just needs flooring & paint. Kitchen & bathrooms are presented "as is" & will require updating; home is priced accordingly. All appliances stay, including washer & dryer. This home is being offered strictly AS-IS, with buyer responsible for village occupancy repairs; (accepting CONVENTIONAL loans only). This opportunity provides the convenience of a move-in ready exterior, with the creativity of personalizing the interior yourself to create your perfect slice of home.
